The Settlement Home, 
Nashville Tenn.
Dr. Graham Taylor,
Dear Sir-- I will leave Nashville Nov. 10th 7:40 A.M., come by way of Louisville Ky., and reach Chicago the 11th at about 5:00 P.M. I will very willingly share a room with another guest or I am very anxious to unclear these two weeks with you. You needs make no provision to meet me for I am familiar with cities and can find my way to the Commons
Yours gratefully
Minerva A Clyee?
